limit.description: The maximum number of items returned. If you don't specify a value, the default is up to 50 items.

nextToken.description: The token for the next set of items to return. (You received this token from a previous call.)

statusCode.description: The status code of the export task. Specifying a status code filters the results to zero or more export tasks.

taskId.description: The ID of the export task. Specifying a task ID filters the results to zero or one export tasks.
